to discuss with you.

00:04:27.077 --> 00:04:28.036
Very well.

00:04:54.356 --> 00:04:56.020
Your Highness,
as you are not yet fully recovered,

00:04:56.077 --> 00:04:58.782
may I ask when you will be able
to return to the army?

00:04:59.397 --> 00:05:00.382
What is this?

00:05:01.156 --> 00:05:02.682
General Su, are you

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:04.760
that eager for me
to hand over military command?

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:07.031
I would never dare.

00:05:07.957 --> 00:05:10.840
The front lines are in crisis, and demands
for battle come day and night.

00:05:10.997 --> 00:05:12.820
I truly have no other choice.

00:05:12.877 --> 00:05:14.395
I beg Your Highness to forgive me.

00:05:15.276 --> 00:05:17.020
When General Su says this,

00:05:17.637 --> 00:05:19.920
do you think I am here enjoying leisure,

00:05:20.437 --> 00:05:21.572
or do you think

00:05:22.236 --> 00:05:23.907
I am deliberately avoiding battle?

00:05:23.957 --> 00:05:25.116
Your Highness misunderstands.

00:05:25.317 --> 00:05:27.232
I was never born with grand ambitions.

00:05:27.576 --> 00:05:29.845
Being able to stay in the capital
and protect the one I love

00:05:29.957 --> 00:05:31.332
is already enough for me.

00:05:31.557 --> 00:05:34.495
As for leading troops into battle,
with Your Highness at the front,

00:05:34.716 --> 00:05:36.045
my heart is at ease.

00:06:14.997 --> 00:06:15.717
Ru.

00:06:16.437 --> 00:06:17.332
Stay.

00:06:17.796 --> 00:06:19.570
I can give up everything for you.

00:06:21.557 --> 00:06:23.356
I do not want the realm
or power anymore.

00:06:24.437 --> 00:06:26.036
Your Highness jokes too easily.

00:06:27.197 --> 00:06:28.676
What you have done,

00:06:28.997 --> 00:06:30.596
do you truly not know in your heart?

00:06:30.975 --> 00:06:33.670
And now you speak
such lofty, righteous words.

00:06:33.796 --> 00:06:35.397
Do you not find them laughable?

00:06:36.637 --> 00:06:37.482
Qingru.

00:06:38.437 --> 00:06:39.870
Give me one more chance.

00:06:40.317 --> 00:06:41.795
Let us begin again.

00:06:41.997 --> 00:06:44.120
Begin again?

00:06:45.796 --> 00:06:46.796
Yuwen Que,

00:06:47.557 --> 00:06:50.116
do you know how I survived
these past three years?

00:06:50.997 --> 00:06:52.195
Every single day,

00:06:52.356 --> 00:06:54.476
I cursed you to die a miserable death.

00:06:55.557 --> 00:06:58.170
And now you come speaking
such hypocritical words of love.

00:06:59.197 --> 00:07:02.007
Do you truly think I am still
the Shen Qingru I once was?

00:07:06.156 --> 00:07:07.036
Qingru.

00:07:08.637 --> 00:07:09.675
What must I do

00:07:09.676 --> 00:07:11.277
for you to return to my side?

00:07:17.596 --> 00:07:18.545
Heng Dao.

00:07:20.276 --> 00:07:21.170
Your Highness.

00:07:21.356 --> 00:07:23.032
Go back and tell His Majesty for me,

00:07:23.350 --> 00:07:26.262
that I am gravely wounded, and must remain
in the capital to recuperate.

00:07:27.036 --> 00:07:29.245
Have Su Changji
take command in my stead.

00:07:29.796 --> 00:07:30.657
Yes.

00:07:35.197 --> 00:07:36.355
Has Su Changji not always

00:07:36.356 --> 00:07:37.877
wanted my position?

00:07:39.757 --> 00:07:41.436
Today is the Gods' Bathing Festival.

00:07:41.437 --> 00:07:43.286
(Gods' Bathing Festival)
By imperial decree of the Emperor,

00:07:43.287 --> 00:07:44.475
the people are permitted

00:07:44.476 --> 00:07:46.355
to celebrate together
while wearing masks.

00:07:46.356 --> 00:07:48.196
When the drums sound three times,

00:07:48.197 --> 00:07:49.957
fated bonds
shall be sealed for this life.

00:07:49.997 --> 00:07:51.756
May all under heaven

00:07:51.757 --> 00:07:54.045
be blessed with good destiny.

00:08:12.837 --> 00:08:13.996
How lively it is.

00:08:26.676 --> 00:08:27.957
Ru.

