(I have inquired for so long,)

00:08:51.337 --> 00:08:53.920
(I finally know His Highness is wearing
the Azure Dragon mask today.)

00:08:54.037 --> 00:08:55.595
(This Gods' Bathing Festival destiny,)

00:08:55.596 --> 00:08:57.157
(I have waited three whole years.)

00:08:57.716 --> 00:08:58.556
(Today,)

00:08:58.716 --> 00:09:00.570
(I must seize His Highness' hand,)

00:09:00.725 --> 00:09:02.165
(and tell him how I truly feel.)

00:09:02.797 --> 00:09:03.757
Sister.

00:09:04.037 --> 00:09:05.515
I just saw that gentleman

00:09:05.516 --> 00:09:07.316
wearing the Azure Dragon mask.

00:09:07.917 --> 00:09:10.397
He was standing beneath
that osmanthus tree.

00:09:26.437 --> 00:09:27.457
Careful.

00:09:51.197 --> 00:09:55.755
Joy belongs to this night,
gentle affection meets its finest hour.

00:09:55.756 --> 00:09:57.956
Remove the mask.

00:10:04.116 --> 00:10:06.436
No wonder you looked
so familiar at the time.

00:10:09.077 --> 00:10:09.956
Your Ladyship?

00:10:10.516 --> 00:10:12.076
General Su?

00:10:18.116 --> 00:10:19.277
Trying to leave?

00:10:22.917 --> 00:10:24.036
This must be fate.

00:10:24.037 --> 00:10:25.707
Everything was part of your design.

00:10:33.917 --> 00:10:34.716
Careful.

00:10:35.717 --> 00:10:38.517
The way you treated me back then,
did you ever show a shred of sincerity?

00:10:38.596 --> 00:10:39.597
Sincerity?

00:10:39.716 --> 00:10:41.316
You dare speak of sincerity?

00:10:42.037 --> 00:10:43.237
Let me ask you again.

00:10:45.677 --> 00:10:46.796
Kill me or flay me,

00:10:47.236 --> 00:10:48.517
I submit to whatever you choose.

00:10:49.236 --> 00:10:50.916
The one thing I regret most in this life

00:10:51.317 --> 00:10:52.556
is ever believing you.

00:11:44.876 --> 00:11:46.316
Is it really so easy

00:11:46.317 --> 00:11:48.115
to enter someone's heart
and then walk away?

00:11:48.116 --> 00:11:49.820
You slaughtered my entire family.

00:11:50.636 --> 00:11:52.956
What right do you have
to speak to me of sincerity?

00:11:55.116 --> 00:11:55.796
Ru.

00:11:56.236 --> 00:11:58.107
I will uncover the truth.

00:11:58.476 --> 00:12:00.020
I will personally kill your enemy.

00:12:00.876 --> 00:12:01.820
Kill!